				<p>We are six college students looking for the adventure that Charlie would have loved and joined us on. We wish to embody the fellowship Charlie so dearly took to heart and live it for four months on the trail. This trip will no doubt pose great physical and mental challenges, but we hope to emerge with a greater understanding of what we are capable of as individuals and the great accomplishments that come from a unified body and purpose.<br /><span class="tiny">Click a name to learn more about a crew member.</span></p>
